Class LiBasePostModel

    public class LiBasePostModel
extends java.lang.Object
implements LiPostModel
    Created by kunal.shrivastava on 10/26/16.

    Base class for post request model, implement LiPostModel. This class provides implementation of toJsonString() method and toJson() method, to help in serialization and deserialization of post model object. All post request model must extend this base class, to take advantage of serialization and deserialization.
